OL,5, Two former heads of the civil service  
OL,6, have criticised Liz Truss for sacking  
OL,7, the top official at the Treasury within
OL,8, days of becoming prime minister.       
OL,10,FSir Tom Scholar was fired this week - a
OL,11,Fmove seen as part of a pledge by Ms    
OL,12,FTruss to change "Treasury orthodoxy".  
OL,14,FFormer cabinet secretaries Lord Butler 
OL,15,Fand Lord O'Donnell criticised the      
OL,16,Fdecision, saying it compromised civil  
OL,17,Fservice independence.                  
OL,19,FThe Treasury did not directly comment  
OL,20,Fon the remarks.                        
